- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper uses sentiment analysis to enrich the raw stream of tweets.
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper deals with sensitive and controversial topics that may raise cybersecurity and privacy concerns.
- cs.DL (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of machine learning techniques for sentiment analysis and network analysis.
